<h1> <%= @recipe.name %> </h1>

<p>This recipe for <%= @recipe.name %>  is created by <%= @recipe.instructions %> with just <%= @recipe.servings %> serving. </p>
<<p>The course for this recipe is <%= @recipe.course.name %></p>

<%= link_to "Delete this recipe!", recipe_path, method: :delete, data: { confirm: "Are you sure you want to delete this course?"} %>

<%= link_to "Edit this recipe!", edit_recipe_path(@recipe) %>

<%= link_to "Back to the list of recipes!", recipes_path %>
